python:liste513fb1f a fnoi:Implementation,
        fnoi:PythonClass,
        fnoi:PythonFunction ;
    dcterms:description """Built-in mutable sequence.

If no argument is given, the constructor creates a new empty list.
The argument must be an iterable if specified.""" ;
